ick-fleetwood">米克·弗利特伍德</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/peter-frampton">彼得·弗兰普顿。</a></p><p>帕顿此前分享了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/queen">皇后</a>乐队即将发行的专辑中的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-dolly-partons-triumphant-cover-of-queen-we-are-the-champions-3473765">《我们是冠军》</a>的翻唱。</p><p>接下来是由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/judas-priest">Judas Priest</a>的 Rob Halford 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/motley-crue">Mötley Crüe</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nikki-sixx">Nikki Sixx</a>翻唱的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dolly-parton-teams-up-with-judas-priests-rob-halford-and-motley-crue-nikki-sixx-on-new-song-3457153">《Bygones》</a> ，与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/heart">Heart</a>的 Ann Wilson 翻唱的《Magic Man》以及《World On Fire》。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dolly-parton-reveals-why-she-never-let-elvis-presley-cover-i-will-always-love-you-3499292">多莉·帕顿 (Dolly Parton) 的帖子揭示了为什么她从未让埃尔维斯·普雷斯利 (Elvis Presley) 翻唱“我将永远爱你”(I Will Always Love You)，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
